<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Home Settings</title>
        <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/img/favicon.png" type="image/x-icon">

<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
<style>
body {
    background: #f5f6fa;
    font-family: "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
}
.sidebar {
    width: 250px;
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    height: 100vh;
    background: #1e1f26;
    color: #fff;
    padding-top: 20px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    z-index: 2000;
}
.sidebar h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    font-size: 22px;
}
.sidebar a {
    color: #ddd;
    display: block;
    padding: 12px 25px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 16px;
    transition: 0.2s;
}
.sidebar a:hover,
.sidebar a.active {
    background: #272935;
    color: #fff;
}
.main-content {
    margin-left: 250px;
    padding: 40px 30px;
}
.section-card {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 15px;
    padding: 25px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    box-shadow: 0 3px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    transition: 0.3s;
}
.section-card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
}
.section-card h4 {
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.section-card img {
    max-height: 200px;
    width: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
}
.section-card input,
.section-card textarea {
    margin-bottom: 15px;
}
.btn-primary, .btn-success, .btn-danger {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
}
.btn i {
    margin-right: 5px;
}
@media (max-width: 992px) {
    .main-content {
        margin-left: 0;
        padding: 20px 15px;
    }
    .sidebar {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        position: relative;
    }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Sidebar -->
<div class="sidebar" id="sidebar">
    <h2>Admin Panel</h2>
  <a href="../dashboard.html"><i class="fa fa-home me-2"></i> Dashboard</a>
    <a href="../show.html" class=""><i class="fa fa-box me-2"></i> Products</a>
    <a href="./aboutSettings.html"><i class="fa fa-users me-2"></i> Settings For About</a>
    <a href="./sell.html"><i class="fa fa-shopping-cart me-2"></i> Change Sell Show</a>
    <a href="./settings.html"><i class="fa fa-chart-line me-2"></i> Home Settings</a>
    <a href="../adminaccount.html"><i class="fa fa-gear me-2"></i> Admin Account</a>
    <form method="post" accept="/admin/logout.html">
<button type="submit">Logout</button></form>
</div>

<!-- Main Content -->
<section class="main-content">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Home Settings</h1>
    <p class="fs-6 mb-4 text-end">
        هنا تستطيع تغيير صورة أو النص الخاص بكل جزء من الموقع، وتحديث الإعلانات والمحتوى بسهولة.
    </p>

    <!-- Add Section Form -->
    <div class="section-card">
        <h4>Add New Section</h4>
        <form action="/sections" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
            <input class="form-control" name="smallTitle" placeholder="Small Title" />
            <input class="form-control" name="bigTitle" placeholder="Big Title" />
            <input class="form-control" name="name" placeholder="Name" />
            <textarea class="form-control" name="description" placeholder="Description" rows="3"></textarea>
            <input class="form-control" type="file" name="image" />
            <button class="btn btn-primary w-100 mt-2" type="submit"><i class="fa fa-plus me-2"></i> Save</button>
        </form>
    </div>

    <hr>

    <!-- All Sections -->
    <h4 class="mb-3">All Sections</h4>
    <div class="row">
        <% sections.forEach(s => { %>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                <div class="section-card">
                    <form action="/sections/<%= s._id %>?_method=PUT" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                        <img src="<%= s.imageUrl %>" class="img-fluid mb-2" />
                        <input class="form-control" name="smallTitle" value="<%= s.smallTitle %>" />
                        <input class="form-control" name="bigTitle" value="<%= s.bigTitle %>" />
                        <input class="form-control" name="name" value="<%= s.name %>" />
                        <textarea class="form-control" name="description" rows="3"><%= s.description %></textarea>
                        <input class="form-control" type="file" name="image" />
                        <button class="btn btn-success w-100 mt-2" type="submit"><i class="fa fa-edit me-2"></i> Edit</button>
                    </form>
                    <form action="/sections/<%= s._id %>?_method=DELETE" method="POST">
                        <button class="btn btn-danger w-100 mt-2" type="submit"><i class="fa fa-trash me-2"></i> Remove</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        <% }) %>
    </div>
</section>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
